#: ../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.14/site-packages/sphinxcontrib_rust/rust_link.py:docstring
#: of sphinxcontrib_rust.rust_link.link:3
msgid ""
"The main difference here is that it will mark any text with brackets as a "
"link, even if there is no reference for it. This allows us to inject links "
"for Rust items in the docs similar to rustdoc. However, it will also make "
"links out of text that is not a Rust item name."
msgstr ""

